<div class="game__menu game__menu--hidden">
    <div class="game__user-info">
        <figure class="avatar">
            <a href="#">
                <img src="static/images/avatar.jpg" class="avatar__image" width="100" height="100" alt="">
            </a>
        </figure>
        <div class="game__stats">
            <h3>Tennis Dimmers</h3>
            <div class="game__modifiers">
                <div class="game__modifier">
                    {% include './icons/agility.svg' %}
                    <p>Agility</p>
                </div>
                <div class="modifier">
                    {% include './icons/jager.svg' %}
                    <p>Jager</p>
                </div>
                <div class="game__modifier">
                    {% include './icons/boost.svg' %}
                    <p>Boost</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BUTTONS -->
    <div class="game__buttons">
        <button class="btn" type="button" data-start>Spielen!</button>
        <button class="btn btn--secondary" type="button" data-rules>About this game</button>
    </div>

    <!-- ABOUT -->
    <div class="game__about-game">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>About</h1>
            <p>Carve your way through the digital MiraSki slopes as you collect the Jäger shots for extra points. Weave past trees, rocks and snow storms in this 3rd person slalom adventure.</p>
            <p>The objective is to get as far as possible without dying. You play as a snowboarder and must navigate between the obstacles on the piste which cause immediate death. You automatically slide down down the mountain, but you can go left or right to any avoid collision with the trees and earn points. Use the arrow keys ([→] [←]) on your keyboard to guide your character down the mountain.</p>
            <p>At the end your score is added to the leaderboard and lists all players that have joined the MiraSki game.</p>
            <p><a href="leaderboard.html">Check out the leaderboard</a></p>
            <button class="btn" class="game__start" type="button" data-start>Spielen!</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
